      <scopecontent id="aspace_sc">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Collection of mounted black and white and color reproductions of Australian paintings. Content varies from original photographic prints to reproductions from magazines and other published sources. Some sections have accompanying clippings folders.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_arr1">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Organized by individual artist name. The individual artist portion is preceded by an Anonymous grouping arranged chronologically.</p>  
      </arrangement>
